caller_intent: The caller is following up on previous messages left for commercial agents at Alliance Insurance and is seeking assistance with an unresolved inquiry.
resolution_steps: Agent acknowledges the caller's attempt to reach commercial agents and confirms they have left messages.
Agent states they will attempt to connect the caller with a commercial agent.
knowledge_required: Understanding of internal processes for connecting callers to commercial agents
Ability to escalate or route calls appropriately
summary: A caller followed up on previous messages to commercial agents at Alliance Insurance, expressing frustration over lack of response. The agent acknowledged the caller's attempts and committed to connecting them with a commercial agent. The call was cut off before resolution.
